        { "type": "component", "title": "서비스 3열 · 제품 5열 그리드 비교", "html": "<div style='margin-bottom:16px'><div class='mc-grid-label'>서비스 — 3열 그리드</div><div class='mc-grid-demo mc-grid-3'><div class='mc-grid-item'>CellBanking</div><div class='mc-grid-item'>Medical Platform</div><div class='mc-grid-item'>Medical AICC</div></div></div><div><div class='mc-grid-label'>제품 — 5열 그리드</div><div class='mc-grid-demo mc-grid-5'><div class='mc-grid-item'>1</div><div class='mc-grid-item'>2</div><div class='mc-grid-item'>3</div><div class='mc-grid-item'>4</div><div class='mc-grid-item'>5</div></div></div>", "css": ".mc-grid-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--sm-content-tertiary);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;margin-bottom:8px}.mc-grid-demo{display:grid;gap:8px}.mc-grid-3{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}.mc-grid-5{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr)}.mc-grid-item{background:var(--sm-background-muted);border:1px solid var(--sm-border-subtle);border-radius:6px;padding:20px 12px;text-align:center;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;color:var(--sm-content-secondary)}@media(max-width:600px){.mc-grid-5{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}" },
