    "interaction": {
      "title": "인터랙션",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "text", "value": "인터랙션의 핵심 원칙은 '필요한 곳에만'. 화려한 모션보다 콘텐츠 전달 효율에 집중합니다." },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "Hover 효과" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "카드 Hover · 버튼 Hover · 링크 Hover", "html": "<div class='mc-hover-demo'><div class='mc-hover-card'><div class='mc-hover-card-inner'>카드 Hover<div class='mc-hover-card-overlay'>View More</div></div></div><button class='mc-hover-btn'>버튼 Hover</button><a class='mc-hover-link'>링크 Hover →</a></div>", "css": ".mc-hover-demo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}.mc-hover-card{width:140px;height:100px;cursor:pointer}.mc-hover-card-inner{position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:var(--sm-background-muted);border-radius:6px;display:grid;place-items:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;overflow:hidden;transition:transform 0.3s}.mc-hover-card-inner:hover{transform:scale(1.03)}.mc-hover-card-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.55);display:grid;place-items:center;color:#fff;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.08em;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.3s}.mc-hover-card-inner:hover .mc-hover-card-overlay{opacity:1}.mc-hover-btn{padding:10px 24px;background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff;border:0;border-radius:4px;font-size:13px;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity 0.2s}.mc-hover-btn:hover{opacity:0.8}.mc-hover-link{font-size:14px;color:var(--sm-content-brand);text-decoration:none;cursor:pointer;transition:opacity 0.2s}.mc-hover-link:hover{opacity:0.6}" },
        { "type": "heading", "value": "전환 애니메이션" },
        { "type": "component", "title": "Opacity / Scale / Background 전환", "html": "<div class='mc-trans-demo'><div class='mc-trans-box mc-trans-opacity'>opacity<br>0.2s</div><div class='mc-trans-box mc-trans-scale'>scale<br>0.3s</div><div class='mc-trans-box mc-trans-bg'>background<br>0.15s</div><div class='mc-trans-box mc-trans-shadow'>shadow<br>0.2s</div></div>", "css": ".mc-trans-demo{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}.mc-trans-box{width:100px;height:80px;display:grid;place-items:center;border-radius:6px;font-size:11px;text-align:center;line-height:1.6;cursor:pointer;border:1px solid var(--sm-border-subtle);background:var(--sm-background-default);color:var(--sm-content-secondary);font-weight:600}.mc-trans-opacity{transition:opacity 0.2s}.mc-trans-opacity:hover{opacity:0.5}.mc-trans-scale{transition:transform 0.3s}.mc-trans-scale:hover{transform:scale(1.1)}.mc-trans-bg{transition:background 0.15s,color 0.15s}.mc-trans-bg:hover{background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff}.mc-trans-shadow{transition:box-shadow 0.2s}.mc-trans-shadow:hover{box-shadow:0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.15)}" },
        { "type": "kv", "title": "인터랙션 인벤토리", "columns": 1, "items": [
          { "label": "카운트업 애니메이션", "value": "스크롤 진입 시 0 → 목표값 카운트업 (duration ~1.5s, ease-out)" },
          { "label": "슬라이더 오토플레이", "value": "15장 이미지 자동 회전 + 수동 넘김" },
          { "label": "로고 컬러 전환", "value": "스크롤 위치에 따라 white → black 전환 (배경 투명도 연동)" },
          { "label": "탭 전환", "value": "즉시 전환 (fade 없음). 연혁 · 제품 LED · R&D 분류에 사용" },
          { "label": "드롭다운", "value": "hover 트리거, 즉시 표시, 부드러운 사라짐" }
